test/testRepacker.py

00001 
00002 # Define a job to test some features of a repacker executable.
00003 # Note that this is in many ways trivial compared to what the
00004 # final repacker executable will need to be.
00005 
00006 # This reads a single streamer file as input and then outputs
00007 # 50 files using 50 PoolOutputModules.  Each output module
00008 # selects events based on a bit in the triggerResults object
00009 # in the input file.
00010 
00011 # Original Author   W. David Dagenhart    19 June 2007
00012 
00013 # This file started as a simple conversion of testRepacker.cfg
00014 # from the old configuration language to PYTHON.
00015 
00016 import FWCore.ParameterSet.Config as cms
